definitions.jiang4: stubborn; unyielding; variant of 強|强[jiang4];
definitions.qiang2: strong; powerful; better; slightly more than; vigorous; violent; best in their category, e.g. see 百強|百强[bai3 qiang2]; variant of 強|强[qiang2];
definitions.qiang3: to force; to compel; to strive; to make an effort; variant of 強|强[qiang3];
